data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Mushrooms of FGBU GPZ Kologrivskij Les name after M.G. Sinicin

Mushrooms Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in FGBU GPZ Kologrivskij Les name after M.G. Sinicin (Russian Federation) consisting of 4 records collected during 1 years between 2011 and 2011.
